BeginningScene:
//want to escape units without KILLING them? do this
RemoveUnit(Sigurd)
RemoveUnit(Alec)
RemoveUnit(Noish)
RemoveUnit(Arden)
//want to change music? just use this
MUSC 0x5
//this is for world map narrations, keep the number the same
Narration(0x8,Ch8_Narration)
CLEAN
//fades in
FADI 16
CAM1 [1,33]
//point where the camera goes
FADU 16
//fades out
Location(Name_Alster)
//little text on the corner
LOAD1 0x1 PlayerUnits
ENUN
//always include an enun after loading units!
LOAD1 0x1 EnemyUnits
ENUN
CAM1 Ovo
FlashCursor(Ovo,16)
//this is incase you want to point to someone specifically, cam for it to look and flash to highlight
GotoPrepScreen
EndEvent

EndingScene:
CleanText(0x9,Placeholder)
MNC2 0x25
EndEvent

Supsis:
