GoMyFEH:
CAM1 [32,12]
CURSOR [32, 12]
STAL 60
REMOVE_CURSORS
//this is to point to a location
EVBIT_T 9
LOAD1 0x1 TheFunny
ENUN
EVBIT_F 9
//camera follows moving guys
Text(Placeholder)
EndEvent

//stand on tile events, pretty standard template unless you need two people
JakeStuck:
CHECK_ACTIVE
SVAL s1 Amid
BNE 0x9000 s1 sC
    Text(Placeholder)
    GOTO 0x9001
LABEL 0x9000
ENUF 0x1B
LABEL 0x9001
EndEvent

